Date: Sat, 30 May 2026 20:49:23 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 69/84] Add HTTP auth callback

A realm asked, "Who goes there?"
We answered through terminal air.
No headers in sight,
No callback too tight,
Just credentials handled with care.
